WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:02:05.520 --> 00:02:06.250
You're back.

00:02:06.480 --> 00:02:07.210
How did it go?

00:02:07.880 --> 00:02:08.940
Tomorrow morning.

00:02:11.720 --> 00:02:13.760
No, it should be this morning.

00:02:14.080 --> 00:02:15.360
It departs at 6:30.

00:02:15.600 --> 00:02:17.040
Military train No. 0712

00:02:17.240 --> 00:02:18.160
will depart from freight track 3.

00:02:18.160 --> 00:02:19.000
The carriages are marked as

00:02:19.000 --> 00:02:20.680
ordnance and special supplies.

00:02:20.680 --> 00:02:22.079
I'll start encoding now.

00:02:23.360 --> 00:02:24.079
Suying,

00:02:24.400 --> 00:02:27.120
send the intel to the Mudanjiang liaison station as soon as possible,

00:02:27.120 --> 00:02:29.400
and have them pass it to the Jingpo Lake guerrillas.

00:02:29.400 --> 00:02:31.120
Also, send the info about train 0712

00:02:31.120 --> 00:02:32.250
to the assault team.

00:02:32.280 --> 00:02:32.920
Okay, Qin.

00:02:32.920 --> 00:02:33.520
Hurry.

00:02:42.120 --> 00:02:42.960
Qin.

00:02:44.320 --> 00:02:45.920
I have a bad feeling.

00:02:47.079 --> 00:02:47.880
What's wrong?

00:02:48.840 --> 00:02:49.840
On my way back,

00:02:50.200 --> 00:02:52.260
I felt like someone was following me.

00:02:52.760 --> 00:02:53.600
Are you sure?

00:02:54.840 --> 00:02:56.000
Did you see clearly?

00:02:56.680 --> 00:02:58.600
It's exactly because I didn't see anyone

00:02:58.600 --> 00:02:59.660
that I feel uneasy.

00:03:00.440 --> 00:03:01.200
Sister Qin.

00:03:01.360 --> 00:03:02.220
How about this?

00:03:02.240 --> 00:03:03.120
You go back first.

00:03:03.120 --> 00:03:04.780
Leave the telegraphing to us.

00:03:05.560 --> 00:03:06.880
I'll leave after you finish sending it.

00:03:06.880 --> 00:03:07.680
Sister Qin,

00:03:08.480 --> 00:03:09.280
listen to me.

00:03:10.000 --> 00:03:11.840
It's very likely that I'm just being paranoid.

00:03:11.840 --> 00:03:12.320
But...

00:03:12.400 --> 00:03:13.600
But we can't afford

00:03:13.600 --> 00:03:14.960
even the slightest loss right now.

00:03:14.960 --> 00:03:15.840
Especially you.

00:03:15.840 --> 00:03:17.500
You are the backbone of us all.

00:03:17.880 --> 00:03:18.560
Besides,

00:03:18.920 --> 00:03:19.800
staying here

00:03:20.360 --> 00:03:21.820
is completely pointless.

00:03:21.840 --> 00:03:22.560
Go.

00:03:24.440 --> 00:03:25.120
Sister Qin.

00:03:26.040 --> 00:03:27.170
Listen to Cheng Lin.

00:03:27.400 --> 00:03:28.160
Go quickly.

00:04:13.000 --> 00:04:13.660
Dongsheng.

00:04:13.800 --> 00:04:15.920
Go back. Cheng Lin and the others are in danger.

00:04:15.920 --> 00:04:16.519
Hurry!

00:04:18.560 --> 00:04:20.440
Excuse me.

00:04:36.560 --> 00:04:37.159
How much left?

00:04:37.159 --> 00:04:37.960
Almost there.

00:04:43.560 --> 00:04:44.280
All sent.

00:04:44.520 --> 00:04:45.680
Open the door!

00:04:47.760 --> 00:04:48.560
Open the door!

00:04:48.920 --> 00:04:49.880
Hurry up!

00:04:50.200 --> 00:04:51.080
Kick the door down!

00:04:51.080 --> 00:04:52.320
Today is a great day.

00:04:52.440 --> 00:04:53.680
Let's go in and drink to the wedding.

00:04:53.680 --> 00:04:54.560
Hurry up!

00:05:01.080 --> 00:05:02.280
Hurry up, Dongsheng!

00:05:02.440 --> 00:05:03.120
Faster!

00:05:12.680 --> 00:05:14.280
Mr. Qin, something's wrong!

00:05:17.640 --> 00:05:18.320
Mr. Qin!

00:05:23.560 --> 00:05:25.020
Quick, burn the codebook!

00:05:30.480 --> 00:05:31.440
What are you doing?

00:05:31.440 --> 00:05:32.240
What are you doing?

00:05:32.240 --> 00:05:34.400
There are only two people and one gun inside.

00:05:34.400 --> 00:05:35.680
Go, charge!

00:05:42.600 --> 00:05:43.659
What are you doing?

00:05:44.080 --> 00:05:45.140
What are you doing?

00:05:45.360 --> 00:05:46.200
Charge!

00:05:46.560 --> 00:05:48.360
Only one gun! Charge!

00:06:04.160 --> 00:06:04.920
Chen Yu!

00:06:06.040 --> 00:06:07.040
Let go of me.

00:06:08.280 --> 00:06:09.760
Cheng Lin and Su Ying are in danger.

00:06:09.760 --> 00:06:10.560
It's too late.

00:06:10.880 --> 00:06:12.280
Qian Yugui and the others have already started fighting.

00:06:12.280 --> 00:06:13.120
You can't save them.

00:06:13.120 --> 00:06:14.200
But I...

00:06:14.320 --> 00:06:15.480
You are the last hope.

00:06:15.480 --> 00:06:16.280
Staying alive

00:06:17.040 --> 00:06:19.240
is more meaningful than anything else.

00:06:34.400 --> 00:06:35.120
Su Ying.

00:06:36.840 --> 00:06:37.360
Are you scared?

00:06:37.360 --> 00:06:38.120
No.

00:06:38.560 --> 00:06:39.890
I'll always be with you.

00:07:04.160 --> 00:07:05.020
Stop fighting.

00:07:05.960 --> 00:07:06.680
Get them.

00:08:42.120 --> 00:08:43.400
You have to be the star

00:08:45.520 --> 00:08:47.040
that shines longer.

00:08:49.440 --> 00:08:50.120
Sister.

00:08:51.160 --> 00:08:53.090
I promise to complete the mission.

00:08:55.880 --> 00:08:56.800
Happy wedding.

00:09:02.360 --> 00:09:04.020
Thank you, Sister. Thank you.

00:09:26.480 --> 00:09:27.320
Sister Qin.

00:09:32.720 --> 00:09:35.250
They were married for less than three months.

00:09:37.640 --> 00:09:39.970
I didn't even have time to give them a gift.

00:09:42.120 --> 00:09:44.720
Suying and Chenglin sacrificed their lives

00:09:45.360 --> 00:09:47.560
to protect the comrades in Jingpo Lake.

00:09:51.160 --> 00:09:53.090
Their blood cannot be shed in vain.

00:09:59.160 --> 00:10:00.000
Sister Qin.

00:10:01.040 --> 00:10:02.160
The radio is gone.

00:10:03.400 --> 00:10:06.000
In case of emergency, we...

00:10:11.480 --> 00:10:12.340
Did you forget?

00:10:13.920 --> 00:10:15.520
We still have another radio.

00:10:17.240 --> 00:10:18.440
It's with my brother.

00:10:19.360 --> 00:10:20.120
Lingzi.

00:10:22.840 --> 00:10:24.240
From now on, on this line,

00:10:25.760 --> 00:10:27.080
it's just the two of us.

00:10:32.360 --> 00:10:33.120
Sister Qin.

00:10:35.920 --> 00:10:37.720
As long as we're both still here,

00:10:38.080 --> 00:10:39.120
our line

00:10:39.840 --> 00:10:41.040
will never be broken.

00:10:42.680 --> 00:10:44.160
We must follow in our comrades' footsteps

00:10:44.160 --> 00:10:45.560
and keep moving forward.

00:10:47.040 --> 00:10:48.770
Be the star that shines longer.

00:10:58.080 --> 00:10:59.480
The codebook is gone too.

00:11:00.680 --> 00:11:01.680
What should we do?

00:11:09.400 --> 00:11:11.260
There is also a dynamic codebook.

00:11:11.680 --> 00:11:12.800
Dynamic codebook?

00:11:14.880 --> 00:11:16.810
The dynamic codebook is in my head.

00:11:17.720 --> 00:11:19.440
I also have an intelligence network.

00:11:19.440 --> 00:11:20.760
If I get intel

00:11:22.040 --> 00:11:23.200
but can't send it out,

00:11:23.200 --> 00:11:24.600
or when I lose my freedom,

00:11:26.120 --> 00:11:27.640
I will use "Moon of the Battlefield"

00:11:27.640 --> 00:11:28.840
to pass intel to you.

00:11:29.440 --> 00:11:30.440
The dynamic code

00:11:30.960 --> 00:11:32.160
is right in this song.

00:11:35.560 --> 00:11:36.760
I will remember that.

00:11:40.760 --> 00:11:42.090
I will tell you right now

00:11:42.640 --> 00:11:44.100
the code for the codebook.

00:11:44.320 --> 00:11:44.800
Okay.

00:11:44.880 --> 00:11:45.480
Let's go.

00:11:59.400 --> 00:12:01.400
Captain Matsuda, please calm down.

00:12:05.720 --> 00:12:06.640
Qian Yugui.

00:12:07.640 --> 00:12:08.970
How dare you deceive me?

00:12:09.920 --> 00:12:10.680
I didn't.

00:12:11.040 --> 00:12:12.040
I didn't.

00:12:12.680 --> 00:12:14.120
A newly severed pinky.

00:12:14.360 --> 00:12:15.820
Do you take me for an idiot?

00:12:17.880 --> 00:12:18.760
Newly severed?

00:12:20.440 --> 00:12:21.880
How come I didn't see it?

00:12:23.320 --> 00:12:24.920
That was an inmate on death row.

00:12:24.920 --> 00:12:26.380
Do you think I didn't know?

00:12:28.880 --> 00:12:30.360
I hate people who lie,

00:12:30.720 --> 00:12:31.480
deceive,

00:12:32.080 --> 00:12:33.010
and fake things.

00:12:33.240 --> 00:12:33.960
Today,

00:12:34.760 --> 00:12:37.120
in front of everyone in the secret service department...

00:12:37.120 --> 00:12:38.880
I'll execute you to set an example.

00:12:38.880 --> 00:12:39.560
Guards!

00:12:39.760 --> 00:12:40.800
Wait, Captain.

00:12:40.880 --> 00:12:42.680
You are a man of your word, right?

00:12:43.280 --> 00:12:45.160
Don't forget our agreement.

00:12:46.000 --> 00:12:48.480
We agreed on seven days.

00:12:49.160 --> 00:12:50.280
It's only been...

00:12:50.600 --> 00:12:53.530
Only four days have passed. We still have three days.

00:12:54.040 --> 00:12:54.880
I admit

00:12:56.480 --> 00:12:57.940
I caught the wrong person.

00:12:58.360 --> 00:13:00.280
But that doesn't mean in the remaining three days

00:13:00.280 --> 00:13:01.740
I won't catch the real one.

00:13:01.960 --> 00:13:02.800
Captain,

00:13:04.280 --> 00:13:05.720
you must keep your word.

00:13:18.720 --> 00:13:19.520
Captain!

00:13:20.200 --> 00:13:21.640
Even if I don't have merit,

00:13:21.640 --> 00:13:22.970
I've still worked hard!

00:13:23.720 --> 00:13:24.920
These past few days,

00:13:25.040 --> 00:13:26.320
didn't we just uncover

00:13:26.640 --> 00:13:28.560
an underground party radio station?

00:13:28.560 --> 00:13:31.220
And we executed two underground party members!

00:13:31.600 --> 00:13:33.000
You and I are

00:13:33.320 --> 00:13:34.720
of one heart and mind,

00:13:35.200 --> 00:13:36.000
coexisting

00:13:36.560 --> 00:13:37.280
and prospering together.